<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>Community Update - <b>My</b>Profile</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 0 !important;
            box-sizing: border-box !important;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif !important;
            background: transparent !important;
            margin: 0 !important;
            padding: 10px !important;
            min-height: 100vh !important;
            -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
            -ms-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px !important;
            margin: 0 auto !important;
            background: #ffffff !important;
            border-radius: 16px !important;
            overflow: hidden !important;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) !important;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            padding: 30px 20px !important;
            text-align: center !important;
            color: white !important;
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0 !important;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 45px !important;
            height: 45px !important;
            margin: 0 auto 16px !important;
            display: block !important;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1) !important;
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 45px !important;
            height: 45px !important;
            object-fit: contain !important;
            display: block !important;
            margin: 0 auto !important;
            filter: brightness(0) invert(1) !important;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px !important;
        }
        
        .update-card {
            background: #f0fdf4 !important;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0 !important;
            border-radius: 12px !important;
            padding: 20px !important;
            margin: 25px 0 !important;
        }
        
        .highlight-item {
            background: #ffffff !important;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            padding: 15px !important;
            margin: 15px 0 !important;
        }
        
        .action-button {
            display: inline-block !important;
            padding: 12px 24px !important;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            font-size: 14px !important;
            margin: 15px 0 !important;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background: #f8f8f8 !important;
            padding: 25px 20px !important;
            text-align: center !important;
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0 !important;
        }
        
        .support-link {
            display: inline-flex !important;
            align-items: center !important;
            gap: 6px !important;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%) !important;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none !important;
            padding: 10px 16px !important;
            border-radius: 8px !important;
            font-weight: 500 !important;
            margin-bottom: 12px !important;
            font-size: 13px !important;
        }
        
        @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
            .header {
                padding: 25px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 25px 15px !important;
            }
            
            .update-card {
                padding: 15px !important;
            }
            
            .highlight-item {
                padding: 12px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background: #f2f2f2; margin: 0; padding: 10px; min-height: 100vh; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;">
    <div class="email-container" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);">
        <div class="header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%); padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; color: white; border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;">
            <div class="logo" style="width: 45px; height: 45px; margin: 0 auto 16px; display: block;">
                <img src="cid:company-logo" alt="<b>My</b>Profile Logo" style="width: 45px; height: 45px; object-fit: contain; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
            </div>
            <h1 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.2; color: white;">üåü Community Update</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; font-weight: 400; color: white;">What's happening in your community</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content" style="padding: 30px 20px;">
            <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #2d3748; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 500;">
                Hi {{firstName}},
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568;">
                Here's what's been happening in the <b>My</b>Profile community this {{updatePeriod}}:
            </p>
            
            <div class="update-card" style="background: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; margin: 25px 0;">
                <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #166534; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    üìä Community Stats
                </h3>
                
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                    <div style="text-align: center; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
                        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #166534;">{{newMembers}}</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">New Members</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
                        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #166534;">{{activeUsers}}</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">Active Users</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
                        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #166534;">{{newConnections}}</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">New Connections</div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="text-align: center; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px;">
                        <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #166534;">{{totalProfiles}}</div>
                        <div style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">Total Profiles</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if highlights}}
            <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin: 25px 0 15px;">üéØ Community Highlights</h3>
            {{#each highlights}}
            <div class="highlight-item" style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 8px;">{{title}}</h4>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px;">{{description}}</p>
                {{#if link}}
                <a href="{{link}}" style="font-size: 13px; color: #000000; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Learn More ‚Üí</a>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/each}}
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if featuredMembers}}
            <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin: 25px 0 15px;">‚≠ê Featured Members</h3>
            {{#each featuredMembers}}
            <div class="highlight-item" style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;">
                    {{#if avatar}}
                    <img src="{{avatar}}" alt="{{name}}" style="width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;">
                    {{else}}
                    <div style="width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">
                        {{substring name 0 1}}
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <div style="flex: 1;">
                        <h4 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 2px;">{{name}}</h4>
                        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;">{{profession}}</p>
                        {{#if achievement}}
                        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #16a34a; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 4px;">üèÜ {{achievement}}</p>
                        {{/if}}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if upcomingEvents}}
            <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin: 25px 0 15px;">üìÖ Upcoming Events</h3>
            {{#each upcomingEvents}}
            <div class="highlight-item" style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; margin-bottom: 8px;">{{title}}</h4>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 8px;">
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">üìÖ {{formatDate date}}</span>
                    <span style="font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280;">üïí {{time}}</span>
                </div>
                <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px;">{{description}}</p>
                {{#if rsvpLink}}
                <a href="{{rsvpLink}}" style="font-size: 13px; color: #000000; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">RSVP Now ‚Üí</a>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/each}}
            {{/if}}
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="{{communityUrl}}" class="action-button" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; margin: 15px 0;">
                    üåü Explore Community
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0;">
                <h4 style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #0369a1; margin-bottom: 8px;">üí° Get More Involved:</h4>
                <ul style="font-size: 13px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.4; margin-left: 15px;">
                    <li>Share your expertise in community discussions</li>
                    <li>Connect with professionals in your field</li>
                    <li>Attend upcoming events and workshops</li>
                    <li>Update your profile to showcase your skills</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin: 20px 0; line-height: 1.6; color: #4a5568; text-align: center;">
                Thank you for being part of our growing community!
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer" style="background: #f8f8f8; padding: 25px 20px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <a href="mailto:support@getmyprofile.online" class="support-link" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000000 0%, #444444 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 13px;">
                üìß Contact Support
            </a>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #444444; line-height: 1.5;">
                This is an automated message from <b>My</b>Profile. Please do not reply to this email.<br>
                If you need assistance, please contact our support team.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 